race.comment: Some talented 3yo's resuming here. SPACE RIDER (1) won well at Moonee Valley in good time first up last preparation, mixing his form thereafter. He's now won both fresh runs and that may be the best time to find him. ROMANTIC ENCOUNTER (3) won narrowly on debut, measuring right up to the G2 Stutt Stakes at start two. Whether 1200m is too sharp is the query but he's talented. CUSTOM (9) takes on the boys having won her maiden well first up last time in. She was close up in two handy races thereafter and has claims. SALTY PEARL (6) went to the paddock a soft winner of the G2 Fillies Classic. She'll get further but can sprint well fresh. JOB DONE (2) has fitness on his side but the level of upside he has left this campaign remains to be seen.
